snippet.title: Polymega Gameplays - Check Mate [PlayStation - PAL]
snippet.description:
Known in Japan as "Simple 1500 Series: Vol.09 - The Chess", this is a budget Chess game for the PlayStation. What else there is to say, other than the fact that I absolutely suck at chess?

Simple Series © D3Publisher
Published in Europe by Midas Interactive
Developed by Success
BIOS Used: Polymega BIOS
